INSERT INTO WeighBridge (
	Docket,
	WB_Docket,
	Date,
	Rego,
	Supplier,
	Operations,
	Coupe,
	Harvestor,
	FPP,
	Gross,
	Tare,
	GMT,
	Grade,
	Length
)
VALUES (
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.DocketVI.toString()}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.WBDocketVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.DateVI.split('T')[0]}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.RegoVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.SupplierVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.OperationsVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.CoupeVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.HarvestorVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.FPPVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.GrossVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.TareVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.GMTVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.GradeVI}}',
	'{{WB_Insert_Form.data.LengthVI}}'
);
